0. Get a VirtualBox : VM installed ( Ubuntu  18.04 - 20.04 )
    - Docker Against VM : non persistent ( unless share volume )
1. Scrape Youtube channels ( subscrpbtion )
Difficulty : 
    - JS rendred ==> scraper with JS CAPABILITIES
    - Scraping tools :
        * Selenium  : OK
        * Requests ( python package ) : X 
        * Others : X
    - Ban : 
        * Tor ( privoxy ) : ( 403 - 413 ) proxy rotation 
    - Recaptcha : Renew the ip + change User Agent


----
Steps :
Create VENV
---
$ python3 -m virtualenv -p python3 .
$ source bin/activate
$ pip install -r requirements.txt
-----
Browse Youtube :
------------
driver.page_source ==> html source for the youtube page 

HTML ------> Selenium + BS4 ( beautiful Soup)  CSS
        |____> lxml xpath




To search in the Net :

$ (Normal User)
# (Root User)

ChromeDriver == Gecko driver 
 
Python --> driver webdriver_manager  --> chrome  
